To magnify or shrink the view in the main 3D world, click on either of the buttons shown below. There are three levels of magnification.  You can also zoom with the mouse scroll wheel.
*[[File:en/Manual/Manual html 628b2aa3.png|Zoom in]] '''Zoom in button''': Zoom in. If the button is disabled, you have reached the maximum magnification level.
*[[File:en/Manual/Manual html m55168bcb.png|Zoom out]] '''Zoom out button''': Zoom out. If the button is disabled, you cannot get a larger view of the gameplay area.

